    #### 1. United States
    - **Defense**: Major Defense Partner status
    - **Agreements**:
      - Civil Nuclear Deal (2008)
      - COMCASA, BECA (defense agreements)
    - **Cooperation**: Trade, technology, Indo-Pacific

    #### 2. Russia
